### 1. Create a new player
POST http://localhost:8080/api/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dobby"
}

### 2. Create another player
POST http://localhost:8080/api/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mattes"
}

### 3. Perform virtual roll (Replace UUID after creation!)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/players/852fd21e-0586-4bd7-b729-33e66c0a636f/roll-virtual

### 4. Perform manual roll (Replace UUID after creation!)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/players/a39184d6-37bc-495a-8048-741ade099d13/roll-manual?d1=1&d2=1&d3=1

### 5. Update penalty chips (Using the new DTO/Record approach)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/players/852fd21e-0586-4bd7-b729-33e66c0a636f
    /penalty-chips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2
}

### 6. Get all players (Verify dice and penalty chips)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players

### 7. Reset all dice for a new round
POST http://localhost:8080/api/players/reset-dice

### 8. Final check: Are all dice cleared (null)?
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players
